# 🚀 fastapi-kit

**The ultimate CLI toolkit for building scalable FastAPI apps — instantly.**
Inspired by Django’s developer experience, `fastapi-kit` helps you scaffold full FastAPI projects and apps using simple commands.

---

## 📦 Features

- `fastapikit startproject myapp` – Scaffold a new FastAPI project
- `fastapikit startapp users` – Create a new modular app
- `fastapikit generate-crud Post` – Auto-generate models, schemas, routes, and CRUD logic
- Follows clean, scalable, production-ready structure
- Extensible for database, Celery, authentication, and more

---

## 🧰 Requirements

- Python 3.8+
- FastAPI installed (installed automatically)

---

## ⚙️ Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/fastapi-kit.git
cd fastapi-kit
pip install -e .
```


